How to install robot framework in Windows and be awesome

  Configuring Python
      1. Install Pyhton v 2.7.9  https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-279/
      2. Add to "Path" to environment variable
      NOTE:
      DON'T DELETE EVERYTHING. JUST ADD ";C:\Python27"
      3. Add \Scripts
      NOTE:
      DON'T DELETE EVERYTHING AGAIN. JUST ADD ";C:\Python27\Scripts"
      4. RESTART CMD
      
    INSTALLING VIRTUAL ENV
      1. pip install virtualenv
      2. pip install virtualenvwrapper-win
      3. mkvirtualenv kat
      
      CREATING SETUP.PY
      1. pip install -e . (installing everything inside setup.py)
